Two persons were yesterday confirmed dead,  while others were injured in two separate road crashes that occured at Alfred Rewane Road, by Marriage Registry intersection, Ikoyi and Unity Bus Stop inward Isheri roundabout, after General Hospital around Isheri area of Igando, Lagos.
   
Isheri zonal head of Lagos State Traffic Management Authority (LASTMA), Mr. Afolalu Gbenga, who confirmed the accident, said two people (pedestrian and passenger) died instantly in the accident involving a PSP truck and Honda Civic car (black APP 79 HF) at Isheri Roundabout immediately after General Hospital.
 
Gbenga said the dead victims were immediately handed over to medical personnel (LASAMBUS) present at the scene of the accident by LASTMA officials. 